                                        1867,
                                        1994,
                                        2164
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "The paper is organized as follows. In the section 2 we provide with the basic notions and facts about synchronization of automata. In the sections 3 and 4 we present basic method of encryption and decryption using our cryptosystem. In the section 5 we state couple of additional improvements to ensure better security. Finally we conclude the paper in the section 6 along with possible further research to the topic."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
